<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<meta name="theme-color" content="#3B82F6" />
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes" />
<title>Offline · Frank Ding Blog</title>
<style>
  :root { color-scheme: dark; }
  html, body { margin: 0; padding: 0; height: 100%; }
  body {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: #0F1428;
    color: #ffffff;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", system-ui, sans-serif;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 40px 20px;
  }
  .box { max-width: 480px; text-align: center; }
  .icon { font-size: 64px; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 20px; opacity: 0.6; }
  h1 {
    font-weight: 600; font-size: 32px; margin: 0 0 12px;
    text-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.18);
  }
  p { margin: 0 0 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; }
  p.note { font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55); margin-bottom: 28px; }
  button {
    padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 13px;
    color: #0A0A0F; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3B82F6 0%, #6366F1 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.35), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit;
  }
  button:active { transform: translateY(1px); }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="box">
    <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">📡</div>
    <h1>You're offline</h1>
    <p>No internet connection detected.</p>
    <p class="note">
      This page isn't cached, so it can't be shown while you're offline.
      Please try again once your connection is back.
    </p>
    <button type="button" onclick="window.location.reload()">Retry</button>
  </main>
</body>
</html>